{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_mt8vxSfHCwnKVJ5ijHJj84gK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！我看到了 Mac Pet 的官网首页。关键信息：\n\n1. **产品定位**: \"Mac Pet — Menu Bar & Notch Pet with Pomodoro Timer for Mac\"\n2. **描述**: \"A pixel pet in your macOS menu bar or notch: Pomodoro timer, activity streaks, and Tamagotchi-style company while you work—always one glance away, never buried in the dock.\"\n3. **Product Hunt 推荐**: Featured on Product Hunt, #4 Product of the Day\n4. **UI 预览**: \n   - MENU BAR 模式: 一只小猫在 macOS 菜单栏中\n   - NOTCH 模式: 小猫在刘海屏凹槽处\n\n这是一个 macOS 独占应用（Menu Bar & Notch），所以 Linux 沙盒肯定无法安装运行。按照 SKILL.md 的降级规则：\n- 产品官网没出当前主机 OS 的安装包（Linux）\n- 这是合法的降级到 web-only 的条件\n\n但我还需要继续浏览官网，找下载链接、定价、功能等页面。让我继续滚动和点击导航。\n\n首先，我需要：\n1. 滚动首页看更多内容\n2. 寻找导航栏中的 Download / Pricing / Features 等链接\n3. 截图更多页面\n\n让我先滚动首页，看看下面有什么内容。同时需要关闭 cookie 弹窗（如果有的话）。\n\n首页已经显示了：\n- 大标题\n- 菜单栏和刘海屏的预览图\n- Product Hunt 徽章\n\n让我继续滚动查看更多内容，然后找导航链接。\n\n先滚动一下。","signature":""}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":53848,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":53848,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"726b0e4a-6150-478e-83db-c6213d6074f0","uuid":"174ee4e0-8993-4b23-b6e7-2081c2139a74"}
