{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_h6ILNBi34SREqkf3Nh6PNd90","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个非常有价值的截图！看到了完整的功能列表：\n\n**WHY CHOOSE MAC PET?**\n\n1. **BUILT-IN POMODORO TIMER**\n   - 集成的番茄钟，可自定义专注和休息时长\n   - 让宠物引导你完成高效工作 session\n\n2. **ACTIVITY TRACKING & STREAKS**\n   - 监控生产力习惯，可视化活动数据\n   - 追踪每日使用、建立 streaks\n   - 5周活动历史，像 contribution graph 一样展示\n\n3. **CHOOSE YOUR PERFECT COMPANION**\n   - 从 sleepy cats 到 energetic dogs\n   - 选择匹配你性格的像素宠物\n   - 每种有独特动画和行为\n\n4. **MACBOOK NOTCH MODE**\n   - 在带刘海的 MacBook 上，宠物可以住在刘海旁边\n   - 无缝黑色背景让刘海看起来像延伸出来容纳宠物\n\n5. **YOUR PRODUCTIVITY PAL**\n   - 像真宠物一样，陪伴你工作\n   - 活跃时显示忙碌，休息时显示睡觉\n   - 微妙提醒保持专注或休息\n\n6. **LIGHTWEIGHT & LOVABLE**\n   - 使用不到 1% CPU\n   - 不会拖慢 Mac\n   - 像真宠物但没有资源负担\n\n让我继续滚动看下载/定价/底部信息。","signature":""}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":61003,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":61003,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"726b0e4a-6150-478e-83db-c6213d6074f0","uuid":"61f2260a-9cb5-4999-ad2e-b441840aa32c"}
